1
00:00:03,670 --> 00:00:04,437
Just use your cute persona

2
00:00:04,438 --> 00:00:05,438
to win people over.

3
00:00:05,439 --> 00:00:06,905
Don't let Hei Yan steal the spotlight.

4
00:00:06,906 --> 00:00:09,441
Girls these days love your type.

5
00:00:09,442 --> 00:00:11,778
You didn't tell me you had a driver.

6
00:00:13,613 --> 00:00:15,013
Well, you're the one who jumped in.

7
00:00:15,715 --> 00:00:17,751
Are you always this quiet?

8
00:00:26,059 --> 00:00:27,961
You didn't sleep well last night.

9
00:00:28,661 --> 00:00:29,981
Your dark circles are pretty bad.

10
00:00:31,030 --> 00:00:32,030
I was nervous.

11
00:00:33,800 --> 00:00:35,440
Nervous about spending the night with me?

12
00:00:35,902 --> 00:00:38,538
I couldn't sleep thinking
about being with you.

13
00:00:43,743 --> 00:00:46,845
Oh, starting the act already? Not bad.

14
00:00:46,846 --> 00:00:47,947
Then let's sing something.

15
00:00:48,415 --> 00:00:49,549
Let's pick a duet.

16
00:00:49,849 --> 00:00:50,949
I saw a lot of fans

17
00:00:50,950 --> 00:00:52,152
wanting us to have a sing-off.

18
00:00:56,256 --> 00:00:57,357
I want to hear you sing.

19
00:01:12,043 --> 00:01:13,356
[some sponsored brand of black tea in a juicebox]

20
00:01:14,340 --> 00:01:15,375
You like this too?

21
00:01:16,810 --> 00:01:17,810
You love it.

22
00:01:20,146 --> 00:01:21,346
If I didn't even know

23
00:01:21,347 --> 00:01:22,414
what your favorite drink was,

24
00:01:22,415 --> 00:01:23,516
how could we be "dating"?

25
00:01:25,318 --> 00:01:27,052
Wow, you're prepared.

26
00:01:27,053 --> 00:01:28,922
You really did your homework.

27
00:01:29,923 --> 00:01:31,624
Fine then, tell me.

28
00:01:31,858 --> 00:01:32,992
What else do I like?

29
00:01:34,427 --> 00:01:36,328
You like cats but you're allergic.

30
00:01:36,329 --> 00:01:38,030
You don't wear slippers because you slip.

31
00:01:38,031 --> 00:01:39,832
You hate pineapple
because it stings your mouth.

32
00:01:39,833 --> 00:01:40,899
You won't eat taro chunks,

33
00:01:40,900 --> 00:01:42,101
but you'll eat it mashed.

34
00:01:42,102 --> 00:01:43,769
You like every color except black.

35
00:01:43,770 --> 00:01:44,537
You love R&amp;B

36
00:01:44,538 --> 00:01:45,818
but hate that you can't sing it.

37
00:01:46,372 --> 00:01:47,474
And...

38
00:01:47,907 --> 00:01:48,908
Okay, that's enough...

39
00:01:56,182 --> 00:01:57,484
Or maybe...

40
00:01:57,951 --> 00:01:59,219
are you actually a fan of mine?

41
00:02:01,297 --> 00:02:02,303
Yeah, right.

42
00:02:02,522 --> 00:02:04,488
I know how to play the part too.

43
00:02:08,761 --> 00:02:09,496
Alright.

44
00:02:09,497 --> 00:02:10,930
Since you're so exhausted,

45
00:02:11,564 --> 00:02:13,132
take a nap. You can lean on me.

46
00:02:13,133 --> 00:02:14,400
You look wiped out.

47
00:02:15,435 --> 00:02:16,435
I'll keep you company.

48
00:02:17,537 --> 00:02:19,705
No thanks, I'm wide awake.

49
00:02:19,706 --> 00:02:21,207
Come on, just do it.

50
00:02:28,915 --> 00:02:30,282
When this gets on camera,

51
00:02:30,283 --> 00:02:31,851
everyone will say how sweet I am.
